description:
This is a 40 minute workout called '40 Minute Total Body Strength Workout with Core Burnout' from the channel FitnessBlender.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.
